originalText.text:
We just “love” her. We had never had the experience of selling property.

Jade was so accommodating to us. She is so professional, patient, proactive and informative.
Always kept in contact and informed us  in all the processes and procedures in the selling of our home.

We wish she could be here in New York City when we purchase our new home. That’s how we truly truly think about her and we are very grateful for having met her.
Dona McNeil and Diane McNeil
